tokens.name: Winiøn #1
tokens.description: Winiøns are mischievøus digital beings from a glitch realm: chaotic, cøllectible creatures that swarm wallets, bring luck, and feed on static, spreading digital mischief across art and code. To own one is to bring good fortune to your wallet. The luck is multiplicative, the more you own, the more the luck (and the mischeif) compounds.
